name: Rebel Flight Suit
Lore: 'Pilot fatigues feature digital technology which can be customized for particular starfighters. Increases interface efficiency with a newly assigned craft.',
Text: 'Deploy on your pilot character. While piloting any starfighter, combat vehicle or shuttle vehicle, that character is considered to be the ''matching pilot'' (pilot adds 2 to maneuver (limit +2) and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise).',
